# Common Interview Mistakes

❌ Thinking `%` returns the quotient.

✅ `%` returns the remainder.

---

❌ Assuming `x++` increments before printing.

✅ `x++` uses the current value first and increments afterwards.

---

❌ Believing Big O measures execution time in seconds.

✅ Big O measures how the running time grows as input size increases.

